pull_request.title: Rewrite endecode to remove internal dependences on OSSL
pull_request.body: Rewrite of encoders / decoders test to hopefully make it much more simpler and removing dependency on internal OSSL structures.

pull_request.title: Add OQS_init and OQS_destroy & GithubCI on PRs
pull_request.body:
- Adds OQS_init() and OQS_destroy() on provider load / teardown (required after https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/liboqs/pull/1431)
- Run GithubCI on PRs

Closes #144

pull_request.body:

This is the initial commit. The following commits should have more weighty code additions.

Fixes #1098.

pull_request.title: Bump oqs-sys/liboqs from `8f38bb4` to `d5be452`
pull_request.body:
Bumps [oqs-sys/liboqs](https://github.com/Open-Quantum-Safe/liboqs) from `8f38bb4` to `d5be452`.

  • 9cf9e10 Use CMake flag for -Werror (#1444)
  • 871f9e2 Initial fetching of MD and Cipher objects from OpenSSL(3) (#1431)
